HPE ProLiant DL Gen9 & Gen10
Secure and versatile rack-optimized servers with a balance of performance, expansion, and manageability across diverse applications.




		               			View Now
							

























HPE Apollo Servers
Purpose-built for high performance computing and big data analytics with breakthrough performance, economy and scalability in a small footprint.




		               			View Now
							

























HPE Integrity Servers
For workloads that define your services, get the highest levels of resiliency balanced with optimized availability, scalability and efficiency.




		               			View Now
							










 










A new HPE infrastructure compute experience
With Hybrid IT, experiences matter. The HPE Compute Experience delivers a cloud-like experience with next-gen HPE rack servers in your data center.















				Learn More
			


























Featured rack servers
Accelerate workloads of all types and sizes with fully customizable and scalable servers.








HPE ProLiant DL560 Gen10.
















HPE ProLiant DL560 Gen10

The high-density 4P/2U scale-up server for business critical computing performance.




HPE ProLiant DL380 Gen10.
















HPE ProLiant DL380 Gen10

The industry-leading 2P/2U server with world-class performance and supreme versatility for multi-workload compute.




HPE ProLiant DL360 Gen10.
















HPE ProLiant DL360 Gen10

The 2P/1U dense compute standard with exceptional flexibility and unmatched expandability for multi-workload environments.




HPE Apollo 6000 Gen10 System.
















HPE Apollo 6000 Gen10 System

An air-cooled HPC solution, optimized for lower total cost of ownership, rack scale efficiency, and exceptional compute performance.




HPE ProLiant DL580 Gen9.
















HPE ProLiant DL580 Gen9

Reliability, serviceability and availability make it the 4P data center standard for base scale-up compute. Form factor: 4U




HPE ProLiant DL160 Gen9.
















HPE ProLiant DL160 Gen9

Entry level with the right balance of storage, efficiency and manageability. Allows a growing enterprise to address various workloads. Form factor: 1U.




HPE ProLiant DL20 Gen9.
















HPE ProLiant DL20 Gen9

The ideal compact platform for growing businesses and service providers running IT infrastructure workloads in space-constrained environments.




HPE ProLiant XL730f Gen9.
















HPE ProLiant XL730f Gen9

Modular for high performance computing with 2 x 2P nodes per tray, up to 144 servers per rack and plenty of throughout options. Form factor: 1U half-width.




HPE Integrity rx2800 i4.
















HPE Integrity rx2800 i4

Reliable and secure for a range of mission critical workloads, with 2U two-socket UNIX. A great fit for both branch offices and data centers.



















				shop Proliant DL Servers
			






















Defend against infrastructure attacks
Your server infrastructure should be your strongest defense, armed with the latest innovations to prevent, detect, and recover from security attacks. It’s no longer adequate to limit security to firewalls.















				Download White Paper
			









































Security company improves video surveillance
BCDVideo, leading video surveillance storage provider, helped its customers increase efficiency, monitor performance, and lower TCO through a custom-built IP video server solution.







Learn How ProLiant Servers Sharpen Video Performance
			















Commanding performance and rock-solid reliability
The HPE ProLiant DL580 Gen9 Server has won the 4P leadership position on both major virtualization benchmarks with the new Intel® Xeon® E7-8890 v4 processors.








Read About ProLiant DL580 Gen9 Server World Records
			









DL380 Gen9 awarded product of the year
CRN announced their 2016 products of the year as voted on by solution providers. The DL380 Gen9 was awarded the overall winner for General Purpose servers due to its performance, management and security capabilities.









Learn About ProLiant DL380 Gen 9 CRN Award
			






























