Hewlett Packard Enterprise

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Hewlett Packard Enterprise Company





Type

Public


Traded as



NYSE: HPE
S&P 500 component





Industry
Information technology


Predecessor
Hewlett-Packard


Founded
November 1, 2015; 20 months ago (2015-11-01)


