Hewlett-Packard - Wikipedia






















 






Hewlett-Packard

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

This article is about the original company from 1939 to 2015. For the current companies, see HP Inc. and Hewlett Packard Enterprise.
Coordinates: 37°24′49″N 122°08′42″W﻿ / ﻿37.413579°N 122.14508°W﻿ / 37.413579; -122.14508

Hewlett-Packard Company





Last logo of Hewlett-Packard used from 2010 to 2015; now used by HP Inc.



