Featured Switches







Aruba 8400 Core Switch.
















Aruba 8400 Core Switch

A breakthrough in core innovation, the 8400 Switch extends intelligence from access layer to core, simplifying and automating complex network tasks.




Aruba 5400R zl2 Switch Series.
















Aruba 5400R zl2 Switch Series

Get enterprise-class resiliency, flexibility and scalability. HPE Smart Rate multi-gigabit ports deliver high-speed connectivity and bandwidth for the next wave of 802.11ac devices and beyond.




Aruba 3810 Switch Series.
















Aruba 3810 Switch Series

High-performance stackable switches that provide performance and resilency for the mobile-first campus network.




Aruba 2930F Switch Series.
















Aruba 2930F Switch Series

Get performance and ease of use for the enterprise campus, SMB and branch office.




Aruba 2930M Switch Series.
















Aruba 2930M Switch Series

Get performance and scalability for the enterprise campus and SMB.



















	             	    Aruba 3810M Switch Leads the Pack
	             	


A recent Tolly Report  shows how the Aruba 3810M Switch Series delivered better performance with 51% lower latency than the Cisco Catalyst 3850. Benefit from lower initial costs and ongoing savings via  more efficient power usage  and cost-effective support.


